{"tid":1822004,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"影人大頭有咩問題","createTime":"2020-01-12T16:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T12:58:25.000Z","uid":57220,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be481acbed2992d3ae7540a858d545e2d7f043ef","tid":1822004,"uid":57220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:17:11.000Z","msg":"出得街怕咩人影<br />\n話緊你地班黑衫仔啊！"},{"pid":"8538b111bf545aa1e06df040eea61ae58e056c26","tid":1822004,"uid":198590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:17:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">「分化撚」勇武又分，廣告界擺工又分，理大又分。希望大家係檢討而唔係指責</span><br />\n會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#57220 - 蕉皮</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>屠龍小隊原來有槍 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>不過冇開過<br />\n龍鳩毛都未跌一條就柒左</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1775037/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1775037/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>其實勇武出黎做乜柒？識反省未 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>一個二個爭住出黎柒<br />\n今日係和平示威又掉哂戲油彈 <br />\n有咩作用先？你話你行出黎 一個頂十個就話<br />\n又唔係 剩係識鳩黎唔用腦<br />\n又唔聽人勸<br />\n鳩鳩下 仆街</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1774539/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1774539/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>請全部手足聽住 如果唔係廣告界既罷工 香港唔會走到呢一步 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>搞到香港鬼死咁亂 都不突止<br />\n仲要掉器油彈 諗住過左區選就肯收手<br />\n點知<br />\n又搞個廣告班鬼頭仔搞罷工 搞死香港<br />\n希望大家咪再同佢地癲 <br />\n感謝！</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1772605/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1772605/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>理工班人係咪戇鳩 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>磨爛蓆，一早出黎就唔撚死咁多手足啦<br />\n睇班柒頭個樣又唔似做勇武<br />\n和理非香港人大撚把啦 洗撚十換一你咩<br />\n話比你班理工戇鳩仔知，你地直接殺死成班手足<br />\n千古罪人呀</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1739535/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1739535/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>今日去出元朗班傻閪死哂未？ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>又要撩班黑社會<br />\n又唔敢出去（得幾百人）<br />\n比人打又嗌生嗌死十足廢柴mk係到叫囂<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fhehe.gif&h=ad0bad84&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fsmile.gif&h=d434394b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1373507/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1373507/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/kBN5bas.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"c60163625dc3bc15cfeb698c920e498ec74c10f8","tid":1822004,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SbddbfG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSbddbfG.png&h=0f8c68cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6858063c74003d6fb330364df95372e0e5e9d3ce","tid":1822004,"uid":177213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"五毛狗"},{"pid":"a2c489ea4396711685afdbb23d558f0317ba9bc3","tid":1822004,"uid":57220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c60163625dc3bc15cfeb698c920e498ec74c10f8","tid":1822004,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SbddbfG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSbddbfG.png&h=0f8c68cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2